# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  LaceraOSINT — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# REQUIRED — Telegram Bot Token (from @BotFather)
BOT_TOKEN=123456789:ABCDefGhIJKlmNoPQRsTUVwxyZ

# REQUIRED — Your Telegram User ID (owner/admin)
# Multiple admins: comma-separated  e.g.  123,456,789
OWNER_ID=123456789

# REQUIRED — LeakOSINT API Token (from /api command in the LeakOSINT bot)
API_TOKEN=987654321:aBcDeFgHiJ

# REQUIRED — PostgreSQL database URL
# Heroku: set automatically. Others: copy from dashboard.
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname

# OPTIONAL — Telegram channels users must join before using bot
# Comma-separated, include @ prefix
REQUIRED_CHANNELS=@YourChannel,@AnotherChannel

# OPTIONAL — Admin username shown on buy button (without @)
ADMIN_USERNAME=yourusername

# OPTIONAL — Daily free search limit per user (default: 4)
DAILY_LIMIT=4

# OPTIONAL — Cooldown between searches in seconds (default: 5)
COOLDOWN_SECONDS=5

# OPTIONAL — Auto-delete result messages after N seconds (default: 120)
AUTO_DELETE_SECS=120

# OPTIONAL — Database connection pool size
DB_MIN_CONN=2
DB_MAX_CONN=20

# OPTIONAL — SSL mode for DB (use 'disable' for local dev)
SSL_MODE=require

# OPTIONAL — LeakOSINT API URL (default is correct)
LEAKOSINT_URL=https://leakosintapi.com/
